	]em
	" with extra storyline, extra items and on a system with a better graphics processor. This run completes the game with 100% item collection, at least as far as the end-of-game display is concerned.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"This run is an improvement over 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/Dragonfangs 
		"Dragonfangs
	]a
	"'s 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=previous work|href=/2458M)
	". It saves about 4 seconds of In-Game time, but uses a new route that removes lots of door transitions, saving about 20 seconds of real time. The previous run used VisualBoyAdvance that runs this game inaccurately fast compared to BizHawk (mGBA core) used here, which is why the movie time appears longer.
	$LF
]div
